title: He Got Kidnapped For A TV Show
itunes:author: Joe Vulpis & Ilya Feddy
description:
Brett Robinson was on CBS's hit TV show Big Brother and had the chance to compete for $500,000. The guys kick back and talk about hazing in the fraternities, 6th years in college, what sparked his massive body build, and waking up in a different state from partying too hard.


Check out Brett on instagram here: https://www.instagram.com/brettwrobinson/?hl=en


Watch our FULL Video Podcast on Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjmqbxZsoH1YwihrGgU1vPA
